TEXT.S:
Chunri Nsgan Chunri o gaga Nsgan Pingtung, kmpraan kana dxgal o 155.55 km², (dxgal dgiyaq o 67.65 km², dxgal pmblxan o 84.62 km²). kmhbragan hiyi o 4,802, sapah o 1,357, seejiq tnpusu 4,590 hiyi, knhbragan hiyi o 96% (Paywang). Paywang ka hbaraw balay alang hini.
nyusan qpahan Nsgan Chunri o niqan 6 alang ni maxal 6. 6 o, Lalekeleke , Kasuga , Seveng , Tjuvecekadan , Kuabar , Kinayiman .
